_:N0e49b85cae214b69bf0959fef69f6e59 <http://schema.org/name> "Social media use" .
_:N101401572f054a51b24621a7fcf43eff <http://schema.org/url> <https://www.gov.uk/assets/frontend/govuk_publishing_components/govuk-logo-b8553f688131fad665e52a8c2df7633f9cd1c0fffb9f69703cc68c728e7b3b74.png> .
